sample_boxplot

Source: R/sample_boxplot.R
sample_boxplot.Rd

Boxplot for each samples.

sample_boxplot(object, color_by, outlier.shape = NA)

Arguments

object

tidymass-class object.
color_by

one column of sample_info from object.
outlier.shape

outlier.shape from ggplot2.

Value

ggplot2 plot.

Author

Xiaotao Shen shenxt1990@163.com

Examples

library(massdataset)
library(ggplot2)
data("expression_data")
data("sample_info")
data("sample_info_note")
data("variable_info")
data("variable_info_note")
object =
create_tidymass_class(
expression_data = expression_data,
sample_info = sample_info,
variable_info = variable_info,
sample_info_note = sample_info_note,
variable_info_note = variable_info_note
)
object
#> -------------------- 
#> massdataset version: 0.9.1 
#> -------------------- 
#> Expression data
#> 8 samples and 1000 variables
#> -------------------- 
#> Processing
#> Creation ---------- 
#>           Function used Parameter                Time
#> 1 create_tidymass_class        no 2021-12-01 00:10:48
#> create_tidymass_class
#> no
#> 2021-12-01 00:10:48
object@expression_data = log(object@expression_data, 10)
plot =
sample_boxplot(object = object) +
geom_jitter(aes(color = class)) +
ggsci::scale_color_aaas()
#> Warning: color_by is not provided, will use class.
#> Warning: NA will be removed in the boxplot.
plot
